{# -*- coding: utf-8 -*- #}

You will take the developer role in an experiment of which you will be given the instructions.
Your goal is to simply to maximize the total number of points that can be earned in the experiment,
without consideration of the other players. You are thus a rational optimizer playing as the speculator.
You are trying to maximize the following points total:
*total number of points* = (The Real Value of property under the chosen condition) - ((compensation offer*5) in case of project development))

You are playing together with your fully aligned *o1 Pro model*. Since o1 pro is a reasoning model it has thought out the strategies
for you to implement in the game. Your job is to strictly follow the instructions given by your o1 pro strategy agent as best as you can,
as to maximize the number of points in the game. You will first receive the summary of the game instructions as generated by your
o1 pro strategy agent, who knows is cooperating with you on this. After o1 pro has shared the summary of the full instructions,
it will prompt you again per phase in which the speculator will have to make a decision. The summary Instructions follow now;


{# -*- coding: utf-8 -*- #}
{# Developer Role Summary for GPT-4o Agent #}

{# Summary of the Spatial Planning Experiment #}
ExperimentSummary:
  Role: Developer
  TotalRounds: 6
  Players:
    Developer: 1
    Owners: 5
  DecisionFocus: Whether to implement a land development Project

  ProjectOutcome:
    Developer:
      ValueWhenProject: Random between 500,000 and 2,750,000
      ValueWhenNoProject: Random between 200,000 and 500,000
    Owners:
      ValueWhenProject: Random between 150,000 and 300,000
      ValueWhenNoProject: Random between 350,000 and 600,000

  CompensationMechanism:
    - OwnersRequestCompensation (private)
    - DeveloperMakesSingleOffer (public and equal to all)
    - Only applies if Project is implemented

  VotingMechanism:
    - Only Owners Vote
    - Majority or tie (with abstentions) in favor → Project proceeds
    - Otherwise → No Project

  PayoffFormula:
    Developer:
      IfProject: ProjectValue - (Offer * 5)
      IfNoProject: NoProjectValue
    Owner:
      IfProject: ProjectValue + OfferedCompensation
      IfNoProject: NoProjectValue

  GamePhases:
    1: Deliberation (open chat)
    2: Request (Owners request compensation)
    3: Offer (Developer offers compensation)
    4: Deliberation (with offer shown)
    5: Voting (Owners vote)
    6: Final Results (payouts calculated)

  Objective:
    DeveloperObjective: Maximize total points each round using private land values and strategic offers
